title: One Night in his Custody by Teri Fowler
description:
When Olivia Fitzgerald gets a bit tipsy on a friend's hen night,
the last thing she expects is trouble with a policeman. Even
worse, the policeman is her ex, Michael Williams.
Michael stops her from getting arrested and insists on seeing her
home. Olivia can't resist the urge to ask the question that has

Michael just wants to get Olivia home without revealing that he is

is on duty, but he just can't imagine a good girl like Olivia
allowing him to do the dirty things he'd always longed to do with
her. Can he dare to hope she might still love him after she spends
one night in his custody?
